UMENGAMELI wezwe, uMnuz Cyril Ramaphosa, kulindeleke ethule inkulumo yakhe ayibhekise ezweni ngo-8 ebusuku. UMENGAMELI wezwe, uMnuz Cyril Ramaphosa, kulindeleke ukuthi ethule inkulumo yakhe ayibhekise ezweni ngo-8 ebusuku. Ngokwesitatimende esifakwe kwi-website yeHhovisi likaMengameli, uRamaphosa uzokwenza le nkulumo namuhla ngo-8 ebusuku. Isitatimende sithe: “Inkulumo izobe imayelana nezinguquko zeCovid-19 eNingizimu Afrika.” Esitatimendeni kuvele ukuthi le nkulumo izobe isakazwa bukhoma eziteshini zeSABC kanjalo nakuzo zonke izinkundla zokuxhumana zekhasi laleli hhovisi, iPresidencyZA.